The Classic Quiz Game, Kaun Banega Crorepati contains 15 Questions which will be presented to you one by one.Answer your way to win 1 Crore and become "The Crorepati".
If you get struck somewhere ,3 Lifelines are available for your help which can be used only once during the course of the game. They are '50-50','Phone a friend','Audience Poll'.
At any point the player can choose to quit the game and walk out with the money he/she has won.
For using the Lifelines just type lifeline and to quit the game type quit.


